amuse.data
Class Feature

java.lang.Object
  amuse.data.Feature
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Feature
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

Feature Object that contains information about a single music feature. This class is used for extracted features as well as for feature extraction itself. Processed features are also stored in this object.
